creator: Zolo
descriptionHtml:
We’re not just an app, we’re the new face of college living.


Download the CampusXP app created to help you design and manage a one-of-a-kind college experience with keeping your holistic development in mind.

This app will help you to concentrate on making the most of your college experience and allow us to remove the wrinkles from your daily living experience.


You can find out what career paths you are suited for, apply for exclusive internships, participate in skill assessments and earn rewards, take personality assessments to better understand yourself, participate in community activities such as treasure hunts, tournaments, and various other games, attend events and conferences, study 24/7 with 1000+ learning resources, and so much more.


These are a few of the features of the app

Enjoy hassle-free living: Simplify your campus stay experience managed by Campus XP.

Exclusive Internship Opportunities: Apply to exclusive internships from top companies around the world and kickstart your career.

Benchmark your Skills: Assess a wide variety of skills and benchmark them against your peer group.

Learn and Explore: Upskill yourself by accessing 1000+ learning resources.

Build your Resume: Craft the perfect resume to nail your dream job.

Find Your Inner Self: Take the first step towards being self-aware using our 50+ personality assessments.

Grow Fitter: Conquer your fitness goals.

Grow Productive: Use tools based on the Pomodoro technique to clear out your to-do list.

It's not all work: Participate in treasure hunts, tournaments, brainteasers, and more.
descriptionShort: A companion app to provide you a rich and hassle-free experience in college
